ABOUT handbook

    This directory contains Zeppe-Lin Handbook, which is used for
    generating Zeppe-Lin website (<https://zeppe-lin.github.io/>) and
    the handbook(7) manual page.

REQUIREMENTS

    Build time:
    * POSIX sh(1p), make(1p) and "mandatory utilities"
    * pod2man(1pm) to generate man page

    Tests:
    * podchecker(1pm) to check POD for errors
    * httpx(1) to check URLs for non-200 response codes

INSTALL

    The shell command "make install-man" should build and install this
    handbook as a manual page.


